    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚试图重新控制非法棕榈种植园</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/indonesia-seeks-to-regain-control-over-illegal-palm-plantations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚计划接管其描述为非法棕榈油种植园的一百万公顷，这是清理全球市场形象并提高国家收入的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/indonesia-seeks-to-regain-control-over-illegal-palm-plantations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 10:28:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着股票集会提高回报，中国生命利润会增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/china-life-profit-jumps-as-stock-rally-boosts-investment-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人寿保险公司表示，由于该国股市的集会增强了投资回报，其保费收入扩大了，去年的利润增长了109％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/china-life-profit-jumps-as-stock-rally-boosts-investment-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 10:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国顶级法院清除了750亿欧元的团结附加费税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/german-top-court-rejects-solidarity-surcharge-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府赢得了一项至关重要的法院裁决，该案件可能从公共库存中剥夺了多达750亿欧元（81亿美元）的税收收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/german-top-court-rejects-solidarity-surcharge-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 09:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银提供了投资银行的限制，以减轻瑞士的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ubs-offers-permanent-investment-bank-cap-to-ease-swiss-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士说，瑞银集团AG的高管建议将其投资银行规模的永久限制写入瑞士法律，以减轻政府对潜在的未来救援的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ubs-offers-permanent-investment-bank-cap-to-ease-swiss-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 07:53:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在数周而不是几个月内权衡铜进口关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，美国对铜进口的关税可能会在几周内，比判决的截止日期提前几个月。在纽约交易的铜升至纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当行业报告指出的是下降美国库存时，石油增益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份行业报告表明美国原油库存下降后，石油越来越高，而市场则权衡了黑海俄罗斯 - 乌克兰停火的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 23:28:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
